name: GETGlobal
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Listen to daily updates from your favorite source. You can just say "Alexa, what's my flash briefing". You can say "Alexa, stop" to exit anytime.
We are a Houston limousine provider and are trying to let our Houstonians know what is going on in their city. We want to shed light on how we can be assistive in our community and how we can bring them to the fun and lively events in our wonderful city. If you need to get in contact with us please find us on the multiple social media accounts or follow this link to our website 
https://www.get-transportation.com/.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
